Description: This data set contains the Cooperative Patent Classification scheme. It is a hierarchical ontology with skos:narrower and skos:broader relations between its about 250 000 nodes (aka "CPC symbols") covering the complete technical domain. It is a refinement of the older International Patent Classification (IPC). CPC is used by major patent offices to classify patent documents.For more details see https://www.cooperativepatentclassification.org/
